title: ICYMI - Nurses Fight COVID-19 and the Anti-Lockdown Movement in North Carolina
itunes:title: ICYMI - Nurses Fight COVID-19 and the Anti-Lockdown Movement in North Carolina
description:
Jordan Klepper talks to a nurse practitioner and a nursing student in North Carolina who have been counter-protesting the backlash against stay-at-home orders.
